Blog posts support Docusaurus Markdown features, such as MDX. tip Use the power of React to create interactive blog posts. <button onClick={() => alert('button clicked!')}>Click me!</button> Copy Click me!

Docusaurus blogging features are powered by the blog plugin. Simply add Markdown files (or folders) to the blog directory. Regular blog authors can be added to authors.yml. The blog post date can be extracted from filenames, such as: 2019-05-30-welcome.md 2019-05-30-welcome/index.md A blog post folder can be convenient to co-locate blog post images: The blog supports tags as well! And if you don't want a blog: just delete this directory, and use blog: false in your Docusaurus config.
Markdown page example You don't need React to write simple standalone pages.
Docusaurus为每一篇博客文章创建一个页面，还有博客索引页面、标签系统、RSS**提要……

创建一个文件在 blog/2021-02-28-greetings.md : blog/2021-02-28-greetings.md ---slug: greetingstitle: Greetings!authors: - name: IO0288 title: Hello url: https://github.com/IO0288 image_url: https://github.com/IO0288.pngtags: [greetings]---Congratulations, you have made your first post!Feel free to play around and edit this post as much you like. Copy 如果blog下的authors.yml存在，则可以不必重复的写那些复杂的内容，只需要调用就好了 blog/2021-02-28-greetings.md ---slug: greetingstitle: Greetings!authors: [IO0288]tags: [greetings]--- Copy 现在可以在 http://localhost:3000/blog/greetings 上看到一篇新的博客文章。
文档是页面组通过以下方式连接: 侧边栏 前/下一个导航 版本管理
创建一个markdown文件在 docs/hello.md : docs/hello.md # HelloThis is my **first Docusaurus document**! Copy 现在可以在 http://localhost:3000/docs/hello 上找到一个新文档。

Docusaurus会自动从 docs 文件夹中创建一个侧边栏。 添加元数据自定义侧边栏标签和位置: docs/hello.md ---sidebar_label: 'Hi!'sidebar_position: 3---# HelloThis is my **first Docusaurus document**! Copy 也可以在 sidebars.js 中显式创建你的侧边栏: sidebars.js module.exports = { tutorialSidebar: [ { type: 'category', label: 'Tutorial',- items: [...],+ items: ['hello'], }, ],}; Copy
在 src/pages 中添加Markdown 或 React文件，以创建独立页面: src/pages/index.js -> localhost:3000/ src/pages/foo.md -> localhost:3000/foo src/pages/foo/bar.js -> localhost:3000/foo/bar

在 src/pages/my-react-page.js 中创建一个文件: src/pages/my-react-page.js import React from 'react';import Layout from '@theme/Layout';export default function MyReactPage() { return (

 );} Copy 现在可以在“http://localhost:3000/my-react-page”上找到一个新页面。
在 src/pages/my-markdown-page.md 创建一个文件: src/pages/my-markdown-page.md # My Markdown pageThis is a Markdown page Copy 现在可以在“http://localhost:3000/my-markdown-page”上找到一个新页面。
Docusaurus支持Markdown和一些额外的功能。

Markdown文档的元数据位于顶部，名为Front Matter: my-doc.md ---id: my-doc-idtitle: My document titledescription: My document descriptionslug: /my-custom-url---## Markdown headingMarkdown text with [links](./hello.md) Copy
支持使用url路径或相对文件路径的常规Markdown链接。 Let's see how to [Create a page](/create-a-page). Copy Let's see how to [Create a page](./create-a-page.md). Copy Result: Let's see how to Create a page.
支持常规Markdown图像。 添加一个图像在 static/img/docusaurus.png ，并显示它在Markdown: ![Docusaurus logo](/img/docusaurus.png) Copy

语法高亮显示支持Markdown代码块。 ```jsx title="src/components/HelloDocusaurus.js“function HelloDocusaurus() { return (

Hello, Docusaurus!

)}``` Copy src/components/HelloDocusaurus.js function HelloDocusaurus() { return

Hello, Docusaurus!

;} Copy

Docusaurus有一个特殊的语法来创建警告和标注: :::tip My tipUse this awesome feature option::::::danger Take careThis action is dangerous::: Copy My tip Use this awesome feature option Take care This action is dangerous

MDX可以使您的文档更交互，并允许使用任何React组件内的Markdown: export const Highlight = ({children, color}) => ( { alert(`You clicked the color ${color} with label ${children}`) }}> {children} );This is Docusaurus green !This is Facebook blue ! Copy This is Docusaurus green ! This is Facebook blue !
Add Markdown or React files to src/pages to create a standalone page: src/pages/index.js -> localhost:3000/ src/pages/foo.md -> localhost:3000/foo src/pages/foo/bar.js -> localhost:3000/foo/bar

Create a file at src/pages/my-react-page.js: src/pages/my-react-page.js import React from 'react';import Layout from '@theme/Layout';export default function MyReactPage() { return (

My React page

 );} Copy A new page is now available at http://localhost:3000/my-react-page.
Create a file at src/pages/my-markdown-page.md: src/pages/my-markdown-page.md # My Markdown pageThis is a Markdown page Copy A new page is now available at http://localhost:3000/my-markdown-page.
Let's discover Docusaurus in less than 5 minutes.
Get started by creating a new site. Or try Docusaurus immediately with docusaurus.new.
Node.js version 14 or above: When installing Node.js, you are recommended to check all checkboxes related to dependencies.

Generate a new Docusaurus site using the classic template. The classic template will automatically be added to your project after you run the command: npm init docusaurus@latest my-website classic Copy You can type this command into Command Prompt, Powershell, Terminal, or any other integrated terminal of your code editor. The command also installs all necessary dependencies you need to run Docusaurus.

Run the development server: cd my-websitenpm run start Copy The cd command changes the directory you're working with. In order to work with your newly created Docusaurus site, you'll need to navigate the terminal there. The npm run start command builds your website locally and serves it through a development server, ready for you to view at http://localhost:3000/. Open docs/intro.md (this page) and edit some lines: the site reloads automatically and displays your changes.
